    "title": "Front Office Manager - Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Grow your career with Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Vijayawada team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions:\nFortune Hotels Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions!",
